---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Valinor Capital — JZ Stafura"
  description="A parody venture capital firm website for a fund backing founders who refuse to inherit broken systems. Tolkien aesthetic. Serious copy. Underground city portfolio."
>
  <div class="back"><a href="/fun/">&#x2190; Fun</a></div>

  <section class="hero">
    <p class="overline">Fun / Parody</p>
    <h1>Valinor Capital</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">The legacy world has a liquidity problem.</p>
    <div class="meta-row">
      <span class="status status-live">Live</span>
      <div class="links">
        <a href="/valinor-capital.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit Valinor Capital &#x2197;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="preview-section">
    <a href="/valinor-capital.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="preview-card">
      <div class="preview-inner">
        <p class="preview-tagline">&ldquo;We back founders who refuse to inherit broken systems.&rdquo;</p>
        <div class="feature-list">
          <span>Tolkien-themed parody VC</span>
          <span>Dark gold aesthetic</span>
          <span>Underground city portfolio</span>
          <span>Libertarian investment thesis</span>
          <span>Co-investors: Grey Havens Partners, Mithril Ventures</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="preview-cta">
        Visit Valinor Capital &#x2197;
      </div>
    </a>
    <p class="preview-note">A parody VC site. Opens in a new tab.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="about">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>Valinor Capital is a fictional venture firm backing founders building infrastructure for a post-surface world. The portfolio includes Underhill (an underground city), ShireChain (logistics), Deepglow (power), and Underrock (mining) &mdash; all supplied by each other in a vertically integrated loop that would make any competition regulator deeply uncomfortable.</p>
    <p>The aesthetic is sincere. The copy is straight-faced. The Tolkien references are relentless. It does not wink.</p>

    <div class="details-grid">
      <div class="detail-block">
        <h3>Stack</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Vanilla HTML / CSS / JS</li>
          <li>Google Fonts (Cinzel, Barlow)</li>
          <li>Scroll animations</li>
          <li>No dependencies</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-block">
        <h3>Disclaimer</h3>
        <p class="detail-desc">Valinor Capital is not a real fund and is not accepting LP commitments. The underground city is not yet habitable. Mithril alloys are fictional. Please do not wire money.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .back { padding: 1.5rem 0 0; }
  .back a { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-muted); text-decoration: none; }
  .back a:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }

  .overline { font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .hero { padding: 2.5rem 0 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.75rem); font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .hero-sub { max-width: 55ch; color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; font-style: italic; }
  .meta-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .status { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.2rem 0.55rem; border: 1px solid; }
  .status-live { color: #16a34a; border-color: rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.3); background: rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.05); }
  .links { display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; }
  .links a { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-muted); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding-bottom: 1px; text-decoration: none; }
  .links a:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }

  .preview-section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }

  .preview-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    border: 1px solid #1C2238;
    background: #070B14;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
  }

  .preview-card:hover {
    border-color: #B8962E;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 24px rgba(184, 150, 46, 0.1);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .preview-inner { padding: 2.5rem 2rem 2rem; }

  .preview-tagline {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #E4DFD5;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 50ch;
  }

  .feature-list { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .feature-list span {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #8A8780;
    border: 1px solid #1C2238;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.65rem;
  }

  .preview-cta {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: #B8962E;
    color: #070B14;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .preview-note { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--color-muted); margin-top: 0.75rem; }

  section.about { padding-bottom: 2rem; }
  .about h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .about p { color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1rem; max-width: 65ch; }

  .details-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .detail-block h3 { font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .detail-block ul { list-style: none; }
  .detail-block li { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-text); padding: 0.2rem 0; }
  .detail-desc { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6; font-style: italic; }
</style>
